  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Direct Anterior Approach (DAA) for Total Hip Arthroplasty (THA): Capsular resection versus
      capsular flap retention.

      Prospective study design comparing clinical data in randomized THA patients who either had
      capsular resection or capsular flap retention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
